metrics_conclusion: In terms of chords and melody, Vien Forest - Pokemon Ranger Shadows of Almia is more complex than the typical song, having above average scores in Chord Complexity, Melodic Complexity, Chord Progression Novelty and Chord-Bass Melody.
key_conclusion: Vien Forest - Pokemon Ranger Shadows of Almia has sections analyzed in the following keys: B♭ Mixolydian, B♭ Major,  and G Phrygian.  Click on the linked cheat sheets for popular chords, chord progressions, downloadable midi files and more!
